You must make an important choice." In 2001, Beijing won the bid to host the Olympics, and the nation celebrated.<br> However, as one of the largest sources of pollution in Beijing, Shougang is under pressure to relocate. With the government's and the public's growing demands for improved air quality, you must make a crucial decision. [[Support Relocation|approval ]] [[Oppose Relocation|Oppose Relocation]] <img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/yuankakala/twine-audio/7729eed672960d90603fc433e9f6ddb4a26c205e/worker.jpg" width="200px"> You are a worker at Shougang. In 2001, Beijing successfully won the Olympic bid, but Shougang now faces the possibility of relocation. [[Continue|继续]] Concerned about job security and your livelihood, you’ve been following the ongoing discussions about the factory’s relocation. Do you support or oppose the move? [[Support the relocation|Support ]] [[Oppose the relocation|oppose ]]<img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/yuankakala/twine-audio/7729eed672960d90603fc433e9f6ddb4a26c205e/scientist.jpg" width="200px"> You are an urban planner at Shougang, tasked with evaluating the factory’s impact on Beijing’s environment. In 2001, Beijing won the bid to host the Olympics, putting environmental concerns in the spotlight. [[Recommend Relocation|建议搬迁]] Propose relocating the factory outside of Beijing in alignment with government policies. [[Recommend Technological Upgrades|Upgrades 建议技术改造]] Advocate for keeping the factory operational while investing in research and innovation to reduce pollution.You’ve decided to support the relocation, but where should it be? [[Relocate to Caofeidian|Relocate to Caofeidian]] Relocation to: <<textbox "$address" "">> <<button "Submit">> <<goto "Support Relocating to {$address}">> <</button>> You’ve decided to relocate Shougang to Caofeidian. Next, you need to decide how to support the workers. [[Provide retraining programs|Retraining Opportunities]] [[Provide compensation|compensation]]You decide to provide retraining for the workers, helping them transition into new roles. Although some feel reluctant, they start to see new hope for the future. [[Ending 0|ending 0]]<img id="background-image" src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/yuankakala/twine-audio/ede003c2682c84eac7ef46e68fc99836f93ee6f6/shougang_start.jpg"> <div class="text-background"> After years of hard work, Shougang successfully relocated to Caofeidian, breathing new life into the company. The workers successfully transitioned to new careers, and the environmental quality in Beijing improved significantly. Shougang's decision was met with widespread approval from the public. <br> As time passed, and the site of the old factory was nearly forgotten, the Olympic rings once again rose proudly at Shougang Park in 2022. Having once made way for both the Olympics and environmental improvements, Shougang has now re-entered the public eye with a fresh, eco-friendly image, becoming a symbol of the blending of industrial heritage and modern civilisation. </div> <<button "restart">> <<goto "restart">> <</button>> <<goto "start">> You suggest relocating Shougang to reduce the environmental pressure on Beijing. [[Continue|Continue2]]You suggested reducing pollution through technological upgrades rather than relocation. [[Five years later|5 years later]]It is now 2006. The technological upgrades have failed to achieve the expected results, leading to increased dissatisfaction from both the public and the government. As a result, environmental issues continue to worsen, with PM2.5 levels severely exceeding safe limits. Despite these challenges, you remain determined to find the best solution and have decided to: [[Continue to resist relocation|resist relocation]] [[Opt to re-plan the relocation|re-plan the relocation]]You decide to support the relocation and move with the factory to Caofeidian, continuing your career in a challenging new environment. In your spare time, you often reflect on your decision. you feel: [[It was the right choice|the right choice]] [[A tinge of regret|regret]] You decide to oppose the relocation and try to find other solutions. [[Consider switching careers|switching careers]]You successfully switch careers by learning new skills and embark on a new life. [[Ending 4|ending 4]]After several years of adjustment, you have settled into a new rhythm in Caofeidian. Your job is stable, and your family has gradually found security. Ten years later, you finally retire with honor, enjoying your later years surrounded by your children and grandchildren. [[Ending 4|ending 4]] Part of Shougang has relocated to {$address}, providing the company with some development opportunities. However, since a portion of the factory remained in Beijing, it has led to increased environmental pollution and the unemployment of some former workers, exacerbating social tensions.
